    CaptionML=[ENU=E.R.-1;
               ENN=E.R.-1];
    OnPreReport=BEGIN
                  IF ReturnYear = 0 THEN
                    ERROR(Text001);

                  StartingDate := DMY2DATE(1,ReturnMonth + 1,ReturnYear);
                  IF ReturnMonth = 11 THEN
                    EndingDate := DMY2DATE(31,ReturnMonth + 1,ReturnYear)
                  ELSE
                    EndingDate := CALCDATE('-1D',DMY2DATE(1,ReturnMonth + 2,ReturnYear));

                  CompanyInformation.GET;
                END;

  }
  DATASET

               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 WHERE(Number=CONST(1));

                               Month := ReturnMonth + 1;
                               IF STRLEN(FORMAT(Month,0)) = 1 THEN
                                 DisplayMonth := '0' + FORMAT(Month,0)
                               ELSE
                                 DisplayMonth := FORMAT(Month,0);
                             END;
                              }

    { 2363;    ;DataItem;ShowOpening         ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 ORDER(Ascending);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               TempER1.RESET;
                               TempER1.DELETEALL;
                               ER1OutputManf.RESET;
                               ER1OutputManf.SETCURRENTKEY("Excise Prod. Posting Group",Unit);
                               ER1OutputManf.SETFILTER("Posting Date",'<=%1',EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 ER1OutputManf.SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);
                               IF ER1OutputManf.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   TempER1.RESET;
                                   TempER1.SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group",ER1OutputManf."Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                                   TempER1.SETRANGE(Unit,ER1OutputManf.Unit);
                                   IF NOT TempER1.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                     TempER1.INIT;
                                     TempER1.TRANSFERFIELDS(ER1OutputManf);
                                     TempER1.INSERT;
                                   END;
                                 UNTIL ER1OutputManf.NEXT = 0;
                               TempER1.SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                               TempER1.SETRANGE(Unit);
                               SETRANGE(Number,1,TempER1.COUNT);
                               TempER1.SETCURRENTKEY("Excise Prod. Posting Group",Unit);
                               IF TempER1.COUNT = 0 THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK
                                 ;
                               TempER1.FINDSET;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  ECCNoItemCategory1@1500000 : Record 16566;
                                BEGIN
                                  QtyCleared1 := 0;
                                  QtyCleared := 0;
                                  QtyManufactured1 := 0;
                                  QtyManufactured := 0;
                                  OpeningStock := 0;
                                  ClosingStock := 0;

                                  IF Number > 1 THEN
                                    TempER1.NEXT;
                                  CompanyInformation.GET;
                                  ER1OutputManf.RESET;
                                  ER1OutputManf.SETFILTER("Posting Date",'<%1',StartingDate);
                                  ER1OutputManf.SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group",TempER1."Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                                  ER1OutputManf.SETFILTER(Unit,'%1',TempER1.Unit);
                                  IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                    ER1OutputManf.SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);
                                  IF ER1OutputManf.FINDSET THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      IF ECCNoItemCategory1.GET(ER1OutputManf."Item No.",ER1OutputManf."E.C.C No.") THEN BEGIN
                                        IF NOT ((ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item"::Intermediate) AND
                                                CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer")
                                        THEN
                                          QtyManufactured1 += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Manufactured";
                                        IF (NOT CheckRemovedAsSuch) AND
                                           NOT ((ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item"::Intermediate) AND
                                                CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" AND (ER1OutputManf."Assessable Value" = 0) AND
                                                (ER1OutputManf.Type = ER1OutputManf.Type::Transfer))
                                        THEN
                                          QtyCleared1 += (ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(with duty)" + ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(without duty)");
                                      END ELSE BEGIN
                                        QtyManufactured1 += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Manufactured";
                                        IF NOT CheckRemovedAsSuch THEN
                                          QtyCleared1 += (ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(with duty)" + ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(without duty)");
                                      END;
                                    UNTIL ER1OutputManf.NEXT = 0;

                                  OpeningStock := QtyManufactured1 + QtyCleared1;
                                  ClosingStock := OpeningStock;
                                  QtyCleared1 := 0;

                                  ER1OutputManf.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                                  IF ER1OutputManf.FINDSET THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      IF ECCNoItemCategory1.GET(ER1OutputManf."Item No.",ER1OutputManf."E.C.C No.") THEN BEGIN
                                        IF NOT ((ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item"::Intermediate) AND
                                                CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer")
                                        THEN
                                          QtyManufactured += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Manufactured";
                                        IF (NOT CheckRemovedAsSuch) AND NOT ((ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item" =
                                                                              ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item"::Intermediate) AND
                                                                             CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" AND (ER1OutputManf."Assessable Value" = 0) AND
                                                                             (ER1OutputManf.Type = ER1OutputManf.Type::Transfer))
                                        THEN
                                          QtyCleared1 += (ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(with duty)" + ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(without duty)");
                                      END ELSE BEGIN
                                        QtyManufactured += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Manufactured";
                                        IF NOT CheckRemovedAsSuch THEN
                                          QtyCleared1 += (ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(with duty)" + ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(without duty)");
                                      END;
                                    UNTIL ER1OutputManf.NEXT = 0;

                                  ClosingStock := ClosingStock + QtyManufactured + QtyCleared1;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1878;1   ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table13755;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Excise Prod. Posting Group,Unit,BED %,AED(GSI) % / Amount,SED % / Amount,SAED % / Amount,CESS % / Amount,NCCD % / Amount,eCess % / Amount,AED (TTA) % / Amount,ADET % / Amount,ADE % / Amount,SHE Cess % / Amount)
                                 WHERE(Excise Prod. Posting Group=FILTER(<>''),
                                       Supplementary=FILTER(No));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);
                               SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group",TempER1."Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                               SETRANGE(Unit,TempER1.Unit);
                               LoopCount1 := 0;

                               TotalCausedBy1 := TempER1."SHE Cess % / Amount";
                               TotalCausedBy2 := TempER1.Unit;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF ECCNoItemCategory.GET("Item No.","E.C.C No.") THEN;
                                  IF ((CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" = TRUE) AND ("Assessable Value" = 0) AND (Type = Type::Transfer) AND
                                      (ECCNoItemCategory."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory."Type of Item"::Intermediate))
                                  THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  LoopCount1 := LoopCount1 + 1;
                                  // RG23APartII.RESET;
                                  // CENVATAmount := 0;
                                  // SEDAmount := 0;

                                  // SAEDAmount := 0;
                                  // CESSAmount := 0;
                                  // NCCDAmount := 0;
                                  // AEDTTAAmount := 0;
                                  // ADETAmount := 0;
                                  // ADEAmount := 0;
                                  // RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                                  // IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                  // RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                                  // RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group","Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                                  // RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Vendor Type",RG23APartII."Vendor Type"::" ");
                                  // IF RG23APartII.FIND('-') THEN
                                  // REPEAT
                                  // CENVATAmount := RG23APartII."Total BED Amount";
                                  // SEDAmount := RG23APartII."Total SED Amount";
                                  // AEDAmount := RG23APartII."Total AED(GSI) Amount";
                                  // AEDTTAAmount := RG23APartII."Total AED(TTA) Amount";
                                  // SAEDAmount := RG23APartII."Total SAED Amount";
                                  // CESSAmount := RG23APartII."Total CESS Amount";
                                  // NCCDAmount := RG23APartII."Total NCCD Amount";
                                  // ADETAmount := RG23APartII."Total ADET Amount";
                                  // ADEAmount := RG23APartII."Total ADE Amount";
                                  // SHECessAmount := RG23APartII."Total SHE Cess Amount";
                                  // UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;
                                  BEDDuty := "BED %";
                                  SEDDuty := "SED % / Amount";
                                  AEDGSIDuty := "AED(GSI) % / Amount";
                                  SAEDDuty := "SAED % / Amount";
                                  OTHDuty := "NCCD % / Amount";
                                  AEDTTADuty := "AED (TTA) % / Amount";
                                  ADEDuty := "ADE % / Amount";
                                  ADETDuty := "ADET % / Amount";
                                  eCessDuty := "eCess % / Amount";
                                  CessDuty := "CESS % / Amount";
                                  SheCessDuty := "SHE Cess % / Amount";

                                  ExcisePostingSetup.SETRANGE("Excise Bus. Posting Group","Excise Bus. Posting Group");
                                  ExcisePostingSetup.SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group","Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                                  ExcisePostingSetup.SETRANGE("From Date",0D,"Posting Date");
                                  IF ExcisePostingSetup.FINDLAST THEN BEGIN
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."BED Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."BED Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      BEDDuty := 0;
                                      CenvatRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."BED Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."BED Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."BED Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      CenvatRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."BED Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."SED Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."SED Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      SEDDuty := 0;
                                      SEDRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."SED Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."SED Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."SED Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      SEDRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."SED Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."AED(GSI) Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."AED(GSI) Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      AEDGSIDuty := 0;
                                      AEDGSIRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."AED(GSI) Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."AED(GSI) Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."AED(GSI) Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit"
                                    THEN
                                      AEDGSIRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."AED(GSI) Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."SAED Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."SAED Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      SAEDDuty := 0;
                                      SAEDRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."SAED Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."SAED Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."SAED Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      SAEDRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."SAED Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."CESS Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."CESS Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      CessDuty := 0;
                                      CessRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."CESS Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."CESS Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."CESS Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      CessRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."CESS Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."NCCD Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."NCCD Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      OTHDuty := 0;
                                      NCCDRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."NCCD Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."NCCD Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."NCCD Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      NCCDRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."NCCD Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."eCess Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."eCess Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      eCessDuty := 0;
                                      eCessRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."eCess Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."eCess Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."eCess Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      eCessRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."eCess Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."AED(TTA) Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."AED(TTA) Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      AEDTTADuty := 0;
                                      AEDTTARateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."AED(TTA) Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."AED(TTA) Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."AED(TTA) Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit"
                                    THEN
                                      AEDTTARateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."AED(TTA) Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."ADET Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."ADET Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      ADETDuty := 0;
                                      ADETRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."ADET Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."ADET Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."ADET Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      ADETRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."ADET Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."ADE Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."ADE Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      ADEDuty := 0;
                                      ADERateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."ADE Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."ADE Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."ADE Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      ADERateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."ADE Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."SHE Cess Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."SHE Cess Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit"
                                    THEN BEGIN
                                      SheCessDuty := 0;
                                      SHECessRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."SHE Cess Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."SHE Cess Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."SHE Cess Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit"
                                    THEN
                                      SHECessRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."SHE Cess Amount Per Unit";
                                  END;
                                  TotalCenvat += "CENVAT Amount";
                                  TotalQuantityRemovedWithDuty += "Quantity Removed(with duty)";
                                  TotalAssessableValue += "Assessable Value";
                                  TotalSEDAmount += "SED Amount";
                                  TotalAEDGSIAmount += "AED (GSI) Amount";
                                  TotalSAEDAmount += "SAED Amount";
                                  TotalCESSAmount += "CESS Amount";
                                  TotalNCCDAmount += "NCCD Amount";
                                  TotaleCESSAmount += "eCESS Amount";
                                  TotalAEDTTAAmount += "AED (TTA) Amount";
                                  TotalADEAmount += "ADE Amount";
                                  TotalADETAmount += "ADET Amount";
                                  TotalQtyRemovedWithoutDuty += "Quantity Removed(without duty)";
                                  TotalSHECessAmount += "SHE Cess Amount";

                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.RESET;
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Invoice No.","Order No.");
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Item No.","Item No.");
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Manually Changed",TRUE);
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE(Type,PostedStrOrderLineDetails.Type::Sale);
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETFILTER("Document Type",'%1|%2',PostedStrOrderLineDetails."Document Type"::Invoice,
                                    PostedStrOrderLineDetails."Document Type"::Order);
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Tax/Charge Code",Text16503);
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Tax/Charge Type",PostedStrOrderLineDetails."Tax/Charge Type"::Excise);
                                  IF PostedStrOrderLineDetails.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                    CENVATAmt += "CENVAT Amount";
                                    SEDAmt += "SED Amount";
                                    AEDGSIAmt += "AED (GSI) Amount";
                                    AEDTTAAmt += "AED (TTA) Amount";
                                    SAEDAmt += "SAED Amount";
                                    CESSAmt += "CESS Amount";
                                    NCCDAmt += "NCCD Amount";
                                    ADETAmt += "ADET Amount";
                                    ADEAmt += "ADE Amount";
                                    eCESSAmt += "eCESS Amount";
                                    SHECessAmt += "SHE Cess Amount";
                                    Amt += "Assessable Value";
                                    QtyRemWithDuty += "Quantity Removed(with duty)";
                                  END;
                                  IF (Type = Type::Sale) OR (Type = Type::Transfer) THEN
                                    "Sale/TransferEntryFound" := TRUE;

                                  IF TotalCausedBy1 = "SHE Cess % / Amount" THEN BEGIN
                                    TotalCausedByFlag1 := FALSE;
                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                    TotalCausedBy1 := "SHE Cess % / Amount";
                                    TotalCausedByFlag1 := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF TotalCausedBy2 = Unit THEN BEGIN
                                    TotalCausedByFlag2 := FALSE;
                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                    TotalCausedBy2 := Unit;
                                    TotalCausedByFlag2 := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF TotalCausedBy3 = "Excise Prod. Posting Group" THEN BEGIN
                                    TotalCausedByFlag3 := FALSE;
                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                    TotalCausedBy3 := "Excise Prod. Posting Group";
                                    TotalCausedByFlag3 := TRUE;
                                  END;

                                  IF TotalCausedByFlag1 THEN BEGIN
                                    TotalCenvat := 0;
                                    TotalQuantityRemovedWithDuty := 0;
                                    TotalAssessableValue := 0;
                                    TotalSEDAmount := 0;
                                    TotalAEDGSIAmount := 0;
                                    TotalSAEDAmount := 0;
                                    TotalCESSAmount := 0;
                                    TotalNCCDAmount := 0;
                                    TotaleCESSAmount := 0;
                                    TotalAEDTTAAmount := 0;
                                    TotalADEAmount := 0;
                                    TotalADETAmount := 0;
                                    TotalQtyRemovedWithoutDuty := 0;
                                    TotalSHECessAmount := 0;
                                    InitialiseVariables;
                                    "Sale/TransferEntryFound" := FALSE;
                                    QtyCleared := 0;
                                  END;

                                  IF TotalCausedByFlag2 THEN BEGIN
                                    InitialiseVariables;
                                    IfPrinted := FALSE;
                                    QtyCleared := 0;
                                    "ERSale/Transfer".RESET;
                                    "ERSale/Transfer".SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                                    IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                      "ERSale/Transfer".SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);
                                    "ERSale/Transfer".SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group","Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                                    "ERSale/Transfer".SETRANGE(Unit,Unit);
                                    "ERSale/Transfer".SETFILTER(Type,'%1|%2',Type::Sale,Type::Transfer);
                                    IF "ERSale/Transfer".FINDFIRST THEN
                                      "Sales/TransferExist" := TRUE
                                    ELSE
                                      "Sales/TransferExist" := FALSE;
                                  END;

                                  IF TotalCausedByFlag3 THEN BEGIN
                                    InitialiseVariables;
                                    QtyCleared := 0;
                                  END;

                                  QtyCleared := 0;
                                  QtyCleared += (TotalQuantityRemovedWithDuty + TotalQtyRemovedWithoutDuty);

                                  QtyCleared := QtyCleared - QtyRemWithDuty;
                                  QtyRemWithDuty := 0;

                                  DisplayAssesibleAmt := TotalAssessableValue - Amt;
                                  IF DisplayAssesibleAmt < 0 THEN
                                    DisplayAssesibleAmt := 0;

                                  DisplayCenvat := TotalCenvat - CENVATAmt;
                                  IF DisplayCenvat < 0 THEN
                                    DisplayCenvat := 0;

                                  DisplaySED := TotalSEDAmount - SEDAmt;
                                  IF DisplaySED < 0 THEN
                                    DisplaySED := 0;

                                  DisplayAEDGSI := TotalAEDGSIAmount - AEDGSIAmt;
                                  IF DisplayAEDGSI < 0 THEN
                                    DisplayAEDGSI := 0;

                                  DisplayAEDTTA := TotalAEDTTAAmount - AEDTTAAmt;
                                  IF DisplayAEDTTA < 0 THEN
                                    DisplayAEDTTA := 0;

                                  DisplayNCCD := TotalNCCDAmount - NCCDAmt;
                                  IF DisplayNCCD < 0 THEN
                                    DisplayNCCD := 0;

                                  DisplaySAED := TotalSAEDAmount - SAEDAmt;
                                  IF DisplaySAED < 0 THEN
                                    DisplaySAED := 0;

                                  DisplayADE := TotalADEAmount - ADEAmt;
                                  IF DisplayADE < 0 THEN
                                    DisplayADE := 0;

                                  DisplayADET := TotalADETAmount - ADETAmt;
                                  IF DisplayADET < 0 THEN
                                    DisplayADET := 0;

                                  DisplayeCess := TotaleCESSAmount - eCESSAmt;
                                  IF DisplayeCess < 0 THEN
                                    DisplayeCess := 0;

                                  DisplaySHECess := TotalSHECessAmount - SHECessAmt;
                                  IF DisplaySHECess < 0 THEN
                                    DisplaySHECess := 0;

                                  DisplayCESS := TotalCESSAmount - CESSAmt;
                                  IF DisplayCESS < 0 THEN
                                    DisplayCESS := 0;

                                  IF ExciseProdPostingGroup.GET("Excise Prod. Posting Group") THEN
                                    Description := COPYSTR(ExciseProdPostingGroup.Description,1,100);
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1500001;2;Column  ;DisplayAssesibleAmt ;
               SourceExpr=DisplayAssesibleAmt }

    { 7365;1   ;DataItem;PrintOpening        ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 ORDER(Ascending)
                                 WHERE(Number=CONST(1));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               IF LoopCount1 <> 0 THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF ExciseProdPostingGroup.GET(TempER1."Excise Prod. Posting Group") THEN
                                    Description := COPYSTR(ExciseProdPostingGroup.Description,1,100);
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1501141;2;Column  ;BlankValue_Control1501141;

               SourceExpr=TempER1."Excise Prod. Posting Group" }

               SourceExpr=OpeningStock }

    { 1170000039;2;Column;PrintOpening_Number;
               SourceExpr=Number }

    { 7417;    ;DataItem;ShowOpening1        ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 ORDER(Ascending);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               TempER1.RESET;
                               TempER1.DELETEALL;
                               ER1OutputManf.RESET;
                               ER1OutputManf.SETCURRENTKEY("Excise Prod. Posting Group",Unit);
                               ER1OutputManf.SETFILTER("Posting Date",'<=%1',EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 ER1OutputManf.SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);
                               IF ER1OutputManf.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF ECCNoItemCategory.GET(ER1OutputManf."Item No.",ER1OutputManf."E.C.C No.") THEN
                                     IF ((CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" = TRUE) AND (ER1OutputManf."Assessable Value" = 0) AND
                                         (ER1OutputManf.Type = ER1OutputManf.Type::Transfer) AND
                                         (ECCNoItemCategory."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory."Type of Item"::Intermediate))
                                     THEN BEGIN
                                       TempER1.RESET;
                                       TempER1.SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group",ER1OutputManf."Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                                       TempER1.SETRANGE(Unit,ER1OutputManf.Unit);
                                       IF NOT TempER1.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                         TempER1.INIT;
                                         TempER1.TRANSFERFIELDS(ER1OutputManf);
                                         TempER1.INSERT;
                                       END;
                                     END;
                                 UNTIL ER1OutputManf.NEXT = 0;
                               TempER1.SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                               TempER1.SETRANGE(Unit);
                               SETRANGE(Number,1,TempER1.COUNT);
                               TempER1.SETCURRENTKEY("Excise Prod. Posting Group",Unit);
                               IF TempER1.COUNT = 0 THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK
                                 ;
                               TempER1.FINDSET;
                               InitialiseVariables;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  ECCNoItemCategory1@1500000 : Record 16566;
                                BEGIN
                                  QtyCleared1 := 0;
                                  QtyCleared := 0;
                                  QtyManufactured1 := 0;
                                  QtyManufactured := 0;
                                  OpeningStock := 0;
                                  ClosingStock := 0;

                                  IF Number > 1 THEN
                                    TempER1.NEXT;
                                  ER1OutputManf.RESET;
                                  ER1OutputManf.SETFILTER("Posting Date",'<%1',StartingDate);
                                  IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                    ER1OutputManf.SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);
                                  ER1OutputManf.SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group",TempER1."Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                                  ER1OutputManf.SETFILTER(Unit,'%1',TempER1.Unit);
                                  IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                    ER1OutputManf.SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);
                                  IF ER1OutputManf.FINDSET THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      IF ECCNoItemCategory1.GET(ER1OutputManf."Item No.",ER1OutputManf."E.C.C No.") THEN BEGIN
                                        IF ((CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" = TRUE) AND (ER1OutputManf."Assessable Value" = 0) AND
                                            (ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item"::Intermediate))
                                        THEN BEGIN
                                          QtyManufactured1 += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Manufactured";
                                          QtyCleared1 += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(with duty)";
                                        END;
                                      END ELSE BEGIN
                                        IF ((CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" = TRUE) AND (ER1OutputManf."Assessable Value" = 0) AND
                                            (ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item"::Intermediate))
                                        THEN BEGIN
                                          QtyManufactured1 += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Manufactured";
                                          QtyCleared1 += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(with duty)";
                                        END;
                                      END;
                                    UNTIL ER1OutputManf.NEXT = 0;

                                  IF QtyCleared1 = 0 THEN
                                    IF ER1OutputManf.FINDSET THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        IF ECCNoItemCategory1.GET(ER1OutputManf."Item No.",ER1OutputManf."E.C.C No.") THEN BEGIN
                                          IF ((CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" = TRUE) AND (ER1OutputManf."Assessable Value" = 0) AND
                                              (ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item"::Intermediate))
                                          THEN
                                            QtyCleared1 += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(without duty)"
                                        END ELSE
                                          IF ((CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" = TRUE) AND (ER1OutputManf."Assessable Value" = 0) AND
                                              (ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item"::Intermediate))
                                          THEN
                                            QtyCleared1 += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(without duty)";
                                      UNTIL ER1OutputManf.NEXT = 0;

                                  OpeningStock2 := QtyManufactured1 + QtyCleared1;
                                  ClosingStock2 := OpeningStock2;
                                  QtyCleared1 := 0;

                                  ER1OutputManf.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                                  IF ER1OutputManf.FINDSET THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      IF ECCNoItemCategory1.GET(ER1OutputManf."Item No.",ER1OutputManf."E.C.C No.") THEN BEGIN
                                        IF ((CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" = TRUE) AND (ER1OutputManf."Assessable Value" = 0) AND
                                            (ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item"::Intermediate))
                                        THEN BEGIN
                                          QtyManufactured += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Manufactured";
                                          QtyCleared1 += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(with duty)";
                                        END;
                                      END;
                                    UNTIL ER1OutputManf.NEXT = 0;

                                  IF QtyCleared1 = 0 THEN
                                    IF ER1OutputManf.FINDSET THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        IF ECCNoItemCategory1.GET(ER1OutputManf."Item No.",ER1OutputManf."E.C.C No.") THEN BEGIN
                                          IF ((CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" = TRUE) AND (ER1OutputManf."Assessable Value" = 0) AND
                                              (ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory1."Type of Item"::Intermediate))
                                          THEN
                                            QtyCleared1 += ER1OutputManf."Quantity Removed(without duty)"
                                        END;
                                      UNTIL ER1OutputManf.NEXT = 0;
                                  ClosingStock2 := ClosingStock2 + QtyManufactured + QtyCleared1;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 4996;1   ;DataItem;<E.R.-1-1>          ;
               DataItemTable=Table13755;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Excise Prod. Posting Group,Unit)
                                 WHERE(Excise Prod. Posting Group=FILTER(<>''),
                                       Supplementary=FILTER(No));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);
                               LoopCount2 := 0;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF ECCNoItemCategory.GET("Item No.","E.C.C No.") THEN;
                                  IF NOT ((CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" = TRUE) AND ("Assessable Value" = 0) AND (Type = Type::Transfer) AND
                                          (ECCNoItemCategory."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory."Type of Item"::Intermediate))
                                  THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;
                                  LoopCount2 := LoopCount2 + 1;

                                  IF TotalCausedBy4 = "Excise Prod. Posting Group" THEN BEGIN
                                    TotalCausedByFlag4 := FALSE;
                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                    TotalCausedBy4 := "Excise Prod. Posting Group";
                                    TotalCausedByFlag4 := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF TotalCausedByFlag4 THEN
                                    QtyCleared := 0;
                                  QtyCleared += -"Quantity Removed(without duty)";
                                  IF ExciseProdPostingGroup.GET("Excise Prod. Posting Group") THEN
                                    Description := COPYSTR(ExciseProdPostingGroup.Description,1,100);
                                END;
                                 }

    { 5719;    ;DataItem;<E.R.-1-2>          ;
               DataItemTable=Table13755;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Excise Prod. Posting Group,Unit)
                                 WHERE(Excise Prod. Posting Group=FILTER(<>''),
                                       Supplementary=FILTER(Yes));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);
                               QtyManufactured := 0;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF Item.GET("Item No.") THEN
                                    IF Item."Excise Prod. Posting Group" = '' THEN
                                      CurrReport.SKIP;
                                  IF ExciseProdPostingGroup.GET("Excise Prod. Posting Group") THEN
                                    Description := COPYSTR(ExciseProdPostingGroup.Description,1,100);

                                  IF TotalCausedBy4 = "Excise Prod. Posting Group" THEN BEGIN
                                    TotalCausedByFlag4 := FALSE;
                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                    TotalCausedBy4 := "Excise Prod. Posting Group";
                                    TotalCausedByFlag4 := TRUE;
                                  END;

                                  IF TotalCausedByFlag4 THEN
                                    InitialiseVariables;

                                  CENVATAmt += "CENVAT Amount";
                                  SEDAmt += "SED Amount";
                                  AEDGSIAmt += "AED (GSI) Amount";
                                  AEDTTAAmt += "AED (TTA) Amount";
                                  SAEDAmt += "SAED Amount";
                                  CESSAmt += "CESS Amount";
                                  NCCDAmt += "NCCD Amount";
                                  ADETAmt += "ADET Amount";
                                  ADEAmt += "ADE Amount";
                                  eCESSAmt += "eCESS Amount";
                                  SHECessAmt += "SHE Cess Amount";

                                  ExcisePostingSetup.SETRANGE("Excise Bus. Posting Group","Excise Bus. Posting Group");
                                  ExcisePostingSetup.SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group","Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                                  ExcisePostingSetup.SETRANGE("From Date",0D,"Posting Date");
                                  IF ExcisePostingSetup.FINDLAST THEN BEGIN
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."BED Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."BED Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      "BED %" := 0;
                                      CenvatRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."BED Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."BED Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."BED Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      CenvatRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."BED Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."SED Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."SED Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      "SED % / Amount" := 0;
                                      SEDRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."SED Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."SED Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."SED Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      SEDRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."SED Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."AED(GSI) Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."AED(GSI) Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      "AED(GSI) % / Amount" := 0;
                                      AEDGSIRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."AED(GSI) Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."AED(GSI) Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."AED(GSI) Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      AEDGSIRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."AED(GSI) Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."SAED Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."SAED Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      "SAED % / Amount" := 0;
                                      SAEDRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."SAED Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."SAED Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."SAED Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      SAEDRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."SAED Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."CESS Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."CESS Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      "CESS % / Amount" := 0;
                                      CessRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."CESS Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."CESS Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."CESS Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      CessRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."CESS Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."NCCD Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."NCCD Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      "NCCD % / Amount" := 0;
                                      NCCDRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."NCCD Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."NCCD Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."NCCD Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      NCCDRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."NCCD Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."eCess Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."eCess Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      "eCess % / Amount" := 0;
                                      eCessRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."eCess Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."eCess Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."eCess Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      eCessRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."eCess Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."AED(TTA) Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."AED(TTA) Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      "AED (TTA) % / Amount" := 0;
                                      AEDTTARateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."AED(TTA) Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."AED(TTA) Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."AED(TTA) Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      AEDTTARateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."AED(TTA) Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."ADET Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."ADET Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      "ADET % / Amount" := 0;
                                      ADETRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."ADET Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."ADET Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."ADET Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      ADETRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."ADET Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."ADE Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."ADE Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      "ADE % / Amount" := 0;
                                      ADERateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."ADE Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."ADE Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."ADE Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      ADERateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."ADE Amount Per Unit";
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."SHE Cess Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."SHE Cess Calculation Type"::"Amount/Unit" THEN BEGIN
                                      "SHE Cess % / Amount" := 0;
                                      SHECessRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."SHE Cess Amount Per Unit";
                                    END;
                                    IF ExcisePostingSetup."SHE Cess Calculation Type" = ExcisePostingSetup."SHE Cess Calculation Type"::"Excise %+Amount/Unit" THEN
                                      SHECessRateSpecific := ExcisePostingSetup."SHE Cess Amount Per Unit";
                                  END;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 3226;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table5745;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Transfer-to Code,Excise Prod. Posting Group,Unit of Measure Code)
                                 WHERE(Excise Prod. Posting Group=FILTER(<>''));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               IF  "Company Information"."Large Tax Payer" = FALSE THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK;

                               TransferShipmentHeader.RESET;
                               TransferShipmentHeader.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 TransferShipmentHeader.SETRANGE("E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               TransferShipmentHeader.SETFILTER("S. No. for RM",'<>%1','');
                               IF TransferShipmentHeader.FINDFIRST THEN
                                 SNoRM1 := TransferShipmentHeader."S. No. for RM";
                               IF TransferShipmentHeader.FINDLAST THEN
                                 SNoRM2 := TransferShipmentHeader."S. No. for RM";

                               TransferShipmentHeader.RESET;
                               TransferShipmentHeader.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 TransferShipmentHeader.SETRANGE("E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               TransferShipmentHeader.SETFILTER("S. No. for IM",'<>%1','');
                               IF TransferShipmentHeader.FINDFIRST THEN
                                 SNoIM1 := TransferShipmentHeader."S. No. for IM";
                               IF TransferShipmentHeader.FINDLAST THEN
                                 SNoIM2 := TransferShipmentHeader."S. No. for IM";

                               CurrReport.CREATETOTALS(Quantity);
                               TotalQuantity := 0;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  TransferShipmentHeader@1500000 : Record 5744;
                                BEGIN
                                  IF Location.GET("Transfer-from Code") THEN
                                    IF ECCNos.GET(Location."E.C.C. No.") THEN
                                      IF NOT ECCNoItemCategory.GET("Item No.",ECCNos.Code) THEN
                                        CurrReport.SKIP;
                                  IF NOT (ECCNoItemCategory."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory."Type of Item"::Intermediate) THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  IF TransferShipmentHeader.GET("Document No.") THEN
                                    IF NOT ((TransferShipmentHeader."Posting Date" >= StartingDate) AND (TransferShipmentHeader."Posting Date" <= EndingDate)) THEN
                                      CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  IF Location.GET("Transfer-from Code") THEN
                                    IF Location."E.C.C. No." <> LocationNo THEN
                                      CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  IF Location.GET("Transfer-to Code") THEN;

                                  IF Item.GET("Item No.") THEN
                                    IF Item."Excise Prod. Posting Group" = '' THEN
                                      CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  ItemLedgEntry.RESET;
                                  ItemLedgEntry.SETRANGE("Document No.","Document No.");
                                  ItemLedgEntry.SETRANGE("Location Code","Transfer-from Code");
                                  IF ItemLedgEntry.FINDFIRST THEN
                                    IF ItemLedgEntry.Quantity < 0 THEN
                                      IF (ItemLedgEntry."BED Amount" <> 0) OR (ItemLedgEntry."Other Duties Amount" <> 0) THEN
                                        CurrReport.SKIP;
                                  TotalQuantity += Quantity;
                                  IF ECCNos.GET(Location."E.C.C. No.") THEN
                                    ECCNo := ECCNos.Code;
                                  IF ExciseProdPostingGroup.GET("Excise Prod. Posting Group") THEN;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1500307;1;Column  ;ECCNo               ;
               SourceExpr=ECCNo }

               SourceExpr=Location.Name + ' ' + Location.Address }

    { 1672;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table13723;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Posting Date)
                                 WHERE(Debit Entry=FILTER(No),
                                       Type of Unit=FILTER(Manufacturer));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               PLACenvatAmount := 0;
                               SEDAmount := 0;
                               AEDAmount := 0;
                               SAEDAmount := 0;
                               CESSAmount := 0;
                               NCCDAmount := 0;
                               AEDTTAAmount := 0;
                               ADETAmount := 0;
                               ADEAmount := 0;
                               PLAeCessAmount := 0;
                               ADCVATAmount := 0;
                               SHECessAmount := 0;
                               PLASHECessAmount := 0;

                               RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Vendor Type",RG23APartII."Vendor Type"::" ");
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",FALSE);
                               IF RG23APartII.FIND('-') THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF RG23APartII.Type = RG23APartII.Type::Sale THEN BEGIN
                                     PLACenvatAmount := PLACenvatAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."BED Debit");
                                     SEDAmount := SEDAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."SED Debit");
                                     AEDAmount := AEDAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit");
                                     SAEDAmount := SAEDAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."SAED Debit");
                                     CESSAmount := CESSAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."CESS Debit");
                                     NCCDAmount := NCCDAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."NCCD Debit");
                                     eCESSAmount := eCESSAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."eCess Debit");
                                     PLAeCessAmount := PLAeCessAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."eCess Debit");
                                     AEDTTAAmount := AEDTTAAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit");
                                     ADETAmount := ADETAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."ADET Debit");
                                     ADEAmount := ADEAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."ADE Debit");
                                     ADCVATAmount := ADCVATAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."ADC VAT Debit");
                                     SHECessAmount := SHECessAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit");
                                     PLASHECessAmount := PLASHECessAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit");
                                   END;
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               RG23CPARTII.RESET;
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Vendor Type",RG23APartII."Vendor Type"::" ");
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",FALSE);
                               IF RG23CPARTII.FIND('-') THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF RG23CPARTII.Type = RG23CPARTII.Type::Sale THEN BEGIN
                                     PLACenvatAmount := PLACenvatAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."BED Debit");
                                     SEDAmount := SEDAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."SED Debit");
                                     AEDAmount := AEDAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Debit");
                                     SAEDAmount := SAEDAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."SAED Debit");
                                     CESSAmount := CESSAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."CESS Debit");
                                     NCCDAmount := NCCDAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."NCCD Debit");
                                     eCESSAmount := eCESSAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit");
                                     PLAeCessAmount := PLAeCessAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit");
                                     AEDTTAAmount := AEDTTAAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Debit");
                                     ADETAmount := ADETAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."ADET Debit");
                                     ADEAmount := ADEAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."ADE Debit");
                                     ADCVATAmount := ADCVATAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Debit");
                                     SHECessAmount := SHECessAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Debit");
                                     PLASHECessAmount := PLASHECessAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Debit");
                                   END;
                                 UNTIL RG23CPARTII.NEXT = 0;

                               SerTaxEntryDetail.RESET;
                               SerTaxEntryDetail.SETCURRENTKEY("Posting Date","Service Tax as Excise");
                               SerTaxEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               SerTaxEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax as Excise",TRUE);
                               SerTaxEntryDetail.CALCSUMS("Applied Amount","Applied eCess Amount");
                               CENVATAmount := CENVATAmount + ABS(SerTaxEntryDetail."Applied Amount");
                               eCESSAmount := eCESSAmount + ABS(SerTaxEntryDetail."Applied eCess Amount");
                               SHECessAmount := SHECessAmount + ABS(SerTaxEntryDetail."Applied SHE Cess Amount");
                             END;
                              }

               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;

                                 WHERE(Number=FILTER(>0));
               MaxIteration=12;
               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  AmountPrinted := FALSE;

                                END;

    { 5027;1   ;DataItem;<Detailed PLA Entry1>;
               DataItemTable=Table16567;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Challan No.,Challan Date,Document No.)
                                 WHERE(Entry Type=FILTER(Application));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 1 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("BED Amount",'<>%1',0);
                               IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 2 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("AED(GSI) Amount",'<>%1',0);
                               IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 3 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("SED Amount",'<>%1',0);
                               IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 4 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("SAED Amount",'<>%1',0);
                               IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 5 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("NCCD Amount",'<>%1',0);
                               IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 6 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Cess Amount",'<>%1',0);
                               IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 7 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("ADET Amount",'<>%1',0);
                               IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 8 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("AED(TTA) Amount",'<>%1',0);
                               IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 9 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("ADE Amount",'<>%1',0);
                               IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 10 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("eCess Amount",'<>%1',0);
                               IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 11 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("SHE Cess Amount",'<>%1',0);
                               IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 12 THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK;
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  PLAEntry2.GET("PLA Entry No.");
                                  IF  (PLAEntry2."Debit Entry" = FALSE) OR (PLAEntry2."Posting Date" < StartingDate) OR (PLAEntry2."Posting Date" > EndingDate)
                                     OR
                                     (PLAEntry2."Type of Unit" <> PLAEntry2."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer) OR
                                     ((LocationNo <> '') AND (PLAEntry2."Location E.C.C. No." <> LocationNo))
                                  THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;
                                  ChangeCounter := ChangeCounter + 1;
                                  IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 1 THEN BEGIN
                                    PLACaption := 'CENVAT';
                                    PLADutyAmount := "BED Amount";
                                    IF NOT AmtPrinted[1] THEN
                                      RGDutyAmount := PLACenvatAmount;
                                    AmtPrinted[1] := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 2 THEN BEGIN
                                    PLACaption := 'AED(GSI)';
                                    PLADutyAmount := "AED(GSI) Amount";
                                    IF NOT AmtPrinted[2] THEN
                                      RGDutyAmount := AEDAmount ;
                                    AmtPrinted[2] := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 3 THEN BEGIN
                                    PLACaption := 'SED';
                                    PLADutyAmount := "SED Amount";
                                    IF NOT AmtPrinted[3] THEN
                                      RGDutyAmount := SEDAmount;
                                    AmtPrinted[3] := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 4 THEN BEGIN
                                    PLACaption := 'SAED';
                                    PLADutyAmount := "SAED Amount";
                                    IF NOT AmtPrinted[4] THEN
                                      RGDutyAmount := SAEDAmount;
                                    AmtPrinted[4] := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 5 THEN BEGIN
                                    PLACaption := 'NCCD';
                                    PLADutyAmount := "NCCD Amount";
                                    IF NOT AmtPrinted[5] THEN
                                      RGDutyAmount := NCCDAmount;
                                    AmtPrinted[5] := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 6 THEN BEGIN
                                    PLACaption := 'Cess';
                                    PLADutyAmount := "Cess Amount";
                                    IF NOT AmtPrinted[6] THEN
                                      RGDutyAmount := CESSAmount;
                                    AmtPrinted[6] := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 7 THEN BEGIN
                                    PLACaption := 'ADET';
                                    PLADutyAmount := "ADET Amount";
                                    IF NOT AmtPrinted[7] THEN
                                      RGDutyAmount := ADETAmount;
                                    AmtPrinted[7] := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 8 THEN BEGIN
                                    PLACaption := 'AED(TTA)';
                                    PLADutyAmount := "AED(TTA) Amount";
                                    IF NOT AmtPrinted[8] THEN
                                      RGDutyAmount := AEDTTAAmount;
                                    AmtPrinted[8] := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 9 THEN BEGIN
                                    PLACaption := 'ADE';
                                    PLADutyAmount := "ADE Amount";
                                    IF NOT AmtPrinted[9] THEN
                                      RGDutyAmount := ADEAmount;
                                    AmtPrinted[9] := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 10 THEN BEGIN
                                    PLACaption := 'eCess';
                                    PLADutyAmount := "eCess Amount";
                                    IF NOT AmtPrinted[10] THEN
                                      RGDutyAmount := PLAeCessAmount;
                                    AmtPrinted[10] := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 11 THEN BEGIN
                                    PLACaption := 'SHE Cess';
                                    PLADutyAmount := "SHE Cess Amount";
                                    IF NOT AmtPrinted[11] THEN
                                      RGDutyAmount := PLASHECessAmount;
                                    AmtPrinted[11] := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer9>".Number = 12 THEN BEGIN
                                    PLACaption := 'ADC VAT';
                                    PLADutyAmount := 0;
                                    IF NOT AmtPrinted[12] THEN
                                      RGDutyAmount := ADCVATAmount;
                                    AmtPrinted[12] := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                  IF (ChangeCounter > 0) AND (NOT AmountPrinted) THEN
                                    AmountPrinted := TRUE;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 4524;    ;DataItem;<PLA Entry1>        ;
               DataItemTable=Table13723;

                                    "BED Credit Amount" + "AED(GSI) Credit" + "SED Credit" + "SAED Credit" + "CESS Credit" + "NCCD Credit" +
                                    "eCess Credit" + "AED(TTA) Credit" + "ADE Credit" + "ADET Credit" + "Excise Charges Credit" + "SHE Cess Credit" ;

                                  UtilizationofPayments +=
                                    "BED Debit Amount" + "AED(GSI) Debit" + "SED Debit" + "SAED Debit" + "CESS Debit" + "NCCD Debit" +
                                    "eCess Debit" + "ADET Debit" + "AED(TTA) Debit" + "ADE Debit" + "SHE Cess Debit";

                                  UtilizationofOtherPayments += "Excise Charges Debit";
                                END;

    { 4858;    ;DataItem;<Integer7>          ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 WHERE(Number=FILTER(1));
               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  PLAEntry1.RESET;
                                  PLAEntry1.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,StartingDate - 1);
                                  IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                    PLAEntry1.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                                  PLAEntry1.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",PLAEntry1."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                                  IF PLAEntry1.FIND('-') THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      PrevChallanpayments +=
                                        PLAEntry1."BED Credit Amount" + PLAEntry1."AED(GSI) Credit" + PLAEntry1."SED Credit" +
                                        PLAEntry1."SAED Credit" + PLAEntry1."CESS Credit" + PLAEntry1."NCCD Credit" +
                                        PLAEntry1."eCess Credit" + PLAEntry1."AED(TTA) Credit" + PLAEntry1."ADE Credit" + PLAEntry1."ADET Credit" +
                                        PLAEntry1."Excise Charges Credit" + PLAEntry1."SHE Cess Credit";

                                      PrevUtilizationofPayments +=
                                        PLAEntry1."BED Debit Amount" + PLAEntry1."AED(GSI) Debit" + PLAEntry1."SED Debit" +
                                        PLAEntry1."SAED Debit" + PLAEntry1."CESS Debit" + PLAEntry1."NCCD Debit" +
                                        PLAEntry1."eCess Debit" + PLAEntry1."ADET Debit" + PLAEntry1."AED(TTA) Debit" + PLAEntry1."ADE Debit" +
                                        PLAEntry1."SHE Cess Debit";

                                      PrevUtilizationofOtherPayments += PLAEntry1."Excise Charges Debit";

                                    UNTIL (PLAEntry1.NEXT = 0);
                                  OpeningBalance :=
                                    OpeningBalance + PrevChallanpayments - PrevUtilizationofPayments - PrevUtilizationofOtherPayments;
                                  TotalAmountAvailable := OpeningBalance + ChallanPayments ;
                                  ClosingBalance := TotalAmountAvailable - UtilizationofPayments - UtilizationofOtherPayments;
                                END;
                                 }
