    { 1432;    ;DataItem;<Integer3>          ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 WHERE(Number=CONST(1));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               // Opening Balances - RG23CPartII
                               OpenCenvatCG := 0.0;
                               OpenAEDCG := 0.0;
                               OpenOTHCG := 0.0;
                               OpeneCESSCG := 0.0;
                               OpenSHEeCESSCG := 0.0;

                               RG23CPARTII.RESET;
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,StartingDate - 1);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               IF RG23CPARTII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF RG23CPARTII."Deferred Claim" = FALSE THEN BEGIN
                                     OpenCenvatCG :=
                                       OpenCenvatCG + RG23CPARTII."BED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPARTII."SED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPARTII."SAED Credit" / 2 +
                                       RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Credit" / 2 + RG23CPARTII."ADET Credit" / 2 - RG23CPARTII."BED Debit" - RG23CPARTII."ADET Debit" -
                                       RG23CPARTII."SED Debit" - RG23CPARTII."SAED Debit" - RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Debit";
                                     OpenAEDCG := OpenAEDCG + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Credit" / 2 - RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                     OpenOTHCG := OpenOTHCG + RG23CPARTII."NCCD Credit" / 2 - RG23CPARTII."NCCD Debit";
                                     OpeneCESSCG := OpeneCESSCG + RG23CPARTII."eCess Credit" / 2 - RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit";
                                     OpenSHEeCESSCG := OpenSHEeCESSCG + RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Credit" / 2 - RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                     OpenADETCG := OpenADETCG + RG23CPARTII."ADE Credit" / 2 - RG23CPARTII."ADE Debit";
                                     OpenADCCG := OpenADCCG + RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Credit" - RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                   END ELSE BEGIN
                                     OpenCenvatCG :=
                                       OpenCenvatCG + RG23CPARTII."BED Credit" + RG23CPARTII."SED Credit" + RG23CPARTII."SAED Credit" +
                                       RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Credit" + RG23CPARTII."ADET Credit" - RG23CPARTII."BED Debit" - RG23CPARTII."ADET Debit" -
                                       RG23CPARTII."SED Debit" - RG23CPARTII."SAED Debit" - RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Debit";
                                     OpenAEDCG := OpenAEDCG + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Credit" - RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                     OpenOTHCG := OpenOTHCG + RG23CPARTII."NCCD Credit" - RG23CPARTII."NCCD Debit";
                                     OpeneCESSCG := OpeneCESSCG + RG23CPARTII."eCess Credit" - RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit";
                                     OpenSHEeCESSCG := OpenSHEeCESSCG + RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Credit" - RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                     OpenADETCG := OpenADETCG + RG23CPARTII."ADE Credit" - RG23CPARTII."ADE Debit";
                                     OpenADCCG := OpenADCCG + RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Credit" - RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                   END;
                                 UNTIL RG23CPARTII.NEXT = 0;

                               // Credit Availed - RG23CPartII
                               CrCenvatTakeCG := 0.0;
                               CrAEDTakeCG := 0.0;
                               CrOTHTakeCG := 0.0;
                               CreCESSTakeCG := 0.0;
                               CrSHEeCESSTakeCG := 0.0;
                               CrADETTakeCG := 0.0;
                               RG23CPARTII.RESET;
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",FALSE);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               IF RG23CPARTII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF ((RG23CPARTII."Vendor Type" = RG23CPARTII."Vendor Type"::" ") OR
                                       (RG23CPARTII."Vendor Type" = RG23CPARTII."Vendor Type"::Manufacturer) OR
                                       (RG23CPARTII."Vendor Type" = RG23CPARTII."Vendor Type"::"First Stage Dealer") OR
                                       (RG23CPARTII."Vendor Type" = RG23CPARTII."Vendor Type"::"Second Stage Dealer")) AND (RG23CPARTII.CVD = FALSE)
                                   THEN BEGIN
                                     IF RG23CPARTII."Deferred Claim" = FALSE THEN BEGIN
                                       CrCenvatTakeCG :=
                                         CrCenvatTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."BED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPARTII."SED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPARTII."SAED Credit" / 2 +
                                         RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Credit" / 2 + RG23CPARTII."ADET Credit" / 2;

                                       CrAEDTakeCG := CrAEDTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Credit" / 2;
                                       CrOTHTakeCG := CrOTHTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."NCCD Credit" / 2;
                                       CreCESSTakeCG := CreCESSTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."eCess Credit" / 2;
                                       CrSHEeCESSTakeCG := CrSHEeCESSTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Credit" / 2;
                                       CrADETTakeCG := CrADETTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."ADE Credit" / 2;
                                       CrADCTakeCG := CrADCTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Credit";
                                     END ELSE BEGIN
                                       DetailExciseDeferrment.RESET;
                                       DetailExciseDeferrment.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                                       DetailExciseDeferrment.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                                       IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                         DetailExciseDeferrment.SETRANGE("E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                                       IF DetailExciseDeferrment.FINDSET THEN
                                         REPEAT
                                           IF ((DetailExciseDeferrment."Vendor Type" = RG23CPARTII."Vendor Type"::" ") OR
                                               (DetailExciseDeferrment."Vendor Type" = DetailExciseDeferrment."Vendor Type"::Manufacturer) OR
                                               (DetailExciseDeferrment."Vendor Type" = DetailExciseDeferrment."Vendor Type"::"First Stage Dealer") OR
                                               (DetailExciseDeferrment."Vendor Type" = DetailExciseDeferrment."Vendor Type"::"Second Stage Dealer")) AND
                                              (DetailExciseDeferrment.CVD = FALSE)
                                           THEN BEGIN
                                             CrCenvatTakeCG :=
                                               CrCenvatTakeCG + DetailExciseDeferrment."BED Amount" + DetailExciseDeferrment."SED Amount" +
                                               DetailExciseDeferrment."SAED Amount" + DetailExciseDeferrment."AED(GSI) Amount" +
                                               DetailExciseDeferrment."ADET Amount" ;
                                             CrAEDTakeCG := CrAEDTakeCG + DetailExciseDeferrment."AED(TTA) Amount" ;
                                             CrOTHTakeCG := CrOTHTakeCG + DetailExciseDeferrment."NCCD Amount";
                                             CreCESSTakeCG := CreCESSTakeCG + DetailExciseDeferrment."eCess Amount";
                                             CrSHEeCESSTakeCG := CrSHEeCESSTakeCG + DetailExciseDeferrment."SHE Cess Amount";
                                             CrADETTakeCG := CrADETTakeCG + DetailExciseDeferrment."ADET Amount";
                                           END ELSE BEGIN
                                             CrCenvatTakeCGImporter :=
                                               CrCenvatTakeCGImporter + DetailExciseDeferrment."BED Amount" + DetailExciseDeferrment."SED Amount" +
                                               DetailExciseDeferrment."SAED Amount" + DetailExciseDeferrment."AED(GSI) Amount" +
                                               DetailExciseDeferrment."ADET Amount" ;
                                             CrAEDTakeCGImporter := CrAEDTakeCGImporter + DetailExciseDeferrment."AED(TTA) Amount" ;
                                             CrOTHTakeCGImporter := CrOTHTakeCGImporter + DetailExciseDeferrment."NCCD Amount";
                                             CreCESSTakeCGImporter := CreCESSTakeCGImporter + DetailExciseDeferrment."eCess Amount";
                                             CrSHEeCESSTakeCGImporter := CrSHEeCESSTakeCGImporter + DetailExciseDeferrment."SHE Cess Amount";
                                             CrADETTakeCGImporter := CrADETTakeCGImporter + DetailExciseDeferrment."ADET Amount";
                                           END;
                                         UNTIL (DetailExciseDeferrment.NEXT = 0);
                                     END;
                                   END
                                   ELSE BEGIN
                                     IF RG23CPARTII."Deferred Claim" = FALSE THEN BEGIN
                                       CrCenvatTakeCGImporter :=
                                         CrCenvatTakeCGImporter + RG23CPARTII."BED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPARTII."SED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPARTII."SAED Credit" / 2 +
                                         RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Credit" / 2 + RG23CPARTII."ADET Credit" / 2;
                                       CrAEDTakeCGImporter := CrAEDTakeCGImporter + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Credit" / 2;
                                       CrOTHTakeCGImporter := CrOTHTakeCGImporter + RG23CPARTII."NCCD Credit" / 2;
                                       CreCESSTakeCGImporter := CreCESSTakeCGImporter + RG23CPARTII."eCess Credit" / 2;
                                       CrSHEeCESSTakeCGImporter := CrSHEeCESSTakeCGImporter + RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Credit" / 2;
                                       CrADETTakeCGImporter := CrADETTakeCGImporter + RG23CPARTII."ADE Credit" / 2;
                                       CrADCTakeCGImporter := CrADCTakeCGImporter + RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Credit";
                                     END
                                   END;
                                 UNTIL RG23CPARTII.NEXT = 0;

                               {RG23CPARTII.RESET;
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE(RG23CPARTII."Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",TRUE);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               IF RG23CPARTII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrSTTakeCG :=
                                     CrSTTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."BED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23CPARTII."SAED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."CESS Debit" +
                                     RG23CPARTII."NCCD Debit" + RG23CPARTII."SED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."ADET Debit" + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Debit" +
                                     RG23CPARTII."ADE Debit" + RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                   CrSTeCessTakeCG := CrSTeCessTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit";
                                 UNTIL(RG23CPARTII.NEXT = 0);   }

                               // Credit Used- InterUnit Transfer
                               IF CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" = TRUE THEN BEGIN
                                 RG23APartII.RESET;
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                                 IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                   RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                                 RG23APartII.SETFILTER(Type,'%1|%2',RG23APartII.Type::" ",RG23APartII.Type::Transfer);
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                                 IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                   REPEAT
                                     CrCenvatTakeIUTransfer :=
                                       CrCenvatTakeIUTransfer + RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" + RG23APartII."SAED Credit" +
                                       RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit";
                                     CrAEDTakeIUTransfer := CrAEDTakeIUTransfer + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit";
                                     CrOTHTakeIUTransfer := CrOTHTakeIUTransfer + RG23APartII."NCCD Credit";
                                     CrCessTakeIUTransfer := CrCessTakeIUTransfer + RG23APartII."eCess Credit";
                                     CrSHECessTakeIUTransfer := CrSHECessTakeIUTransfer + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                     CrADETTTakeIUTransfer := CrADETTTakeIUTransfer + RG23APartII."ADE Credit";
                                     CrADCTakeIUTransfer := CrADCTakeIUTransfer + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit";
                                   UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                                 RG23CPARTII.RESET;
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                                 IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                   RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETFILTER(Type,'%1|%2',RG23APartII.Type::" ",RG23APartII.Type::Transfer);
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                                 IF RG23CPARTII.FINDSET THEN
                                   REPEAT
                                     CrCenvatTakeIUTransfer :=
                                       CrCenvatTakeIUTransfer + RG23CPARTII."BED Credit" + RG23CPARTII."SED Credit" + RG23CPARTII."SAED Credit" +
                                       RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Credit" + RG23CPARTII."ADET Credit";
                                     CrAEDTakeIUTransfer := CrAEDTakeIUTransfer + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Credit";
                                     CrOTHTakeIUTransfer := CrOTHTakeIUTransfer + RG23CPARTII."NCCD Credit";
                                     CrCessTakeIUTransfer := CrCessTakeIUTransfer + RG23CPARTII."eCess Credit";
                                     CrSHECessTakeIUTransfer := CrSHECessTakeIUTransfer + RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                     CrADETTTakeIUTransfer := CrADETTTakeIUTransfer + RG23CPARTII."ADE Credit";
                                     CrADCTakeIUTransfer := CrADCTakeIUTransfer + RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Credit";
                                   UNTIL RG23CPARTII.NEXT = 0;
                               END;

                               // Credit Used - RG23CPartII
                               CrCenvatUsedCG := 0.0;
                               CrAEDUsedCG := 0.0;
                               CrOTHUsedCG := 0.0;
                               CreCESSUsedCG := 0.0;
                               CrSHEeCESSUsedCG := 0.0;
                               CrADETUsedCG := 0.0;

                               RG23CPARTII.RESET;
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE(Type,RG23CPARTII.Type::Sale);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",FALSE);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               IF RG23CPARTII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrCenvatUsedCG :=
                                     CrCenvatUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."BED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."SED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."SAED Debit" +
                                     RG23CPARTII."ADET Debit" + RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Debit";
                                   CrAEDUsedCG := CrAEDUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                   CrOTHUsedCG := CrOTHUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."NCCD Debit";
                                   CreCESSUsedCG := CreCESSUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit";
                                   CrSHEeCESSUsedCG := CrSHEeCESSUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                   CrADETUsedCG := CrADETUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."ADE Debit";
                                   CrADCUsedCG := CrADCUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                 UNTIL RG23CPARTII.NEXT = 0;

                               ExciseAsSTUtlisation.RESET;
                               ExciseAsSTUtlisation.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 ExciseAsSTUtlisation.SETRANGE("ECC No.",LocationNo);
                               ExciseAsSTUtlisation.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               ExciseAsSTUtlisation.SETRANGE("RG Record Type",ExciseAsSTUtlisation."RG Record Type"::RG23A);
                               IF ExciseAsSTUtlisation.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF ((ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type" = ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type"::" ") OR
                                       (ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type" = ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type"::Manufacturer)) AND
                                      (ExciseAsSTUtlisation.CVD = FALSE)
                                   THEN BEGIN
                                     CrSTTakeINManf :=
                                       CrSTTakeINManf + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Bed Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SED Amount" +
                                       ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SAED Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."ADET Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."AED(GSI) Amount" +
                                       ExciseAsSTUtlisation."CESS Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."NCCD Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."AED(TTA) Amount" +
                                       ExciseAsSTUtlisation."ADE Amount" ;
                                     CreCessSTTakeINManf := CreCessSTTakeINManf + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."eCess Amount";
                                     CrSHEeCessSTTakeINManf := CrSHEeCessSTTakeINManf + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SHE Cess Amount";
                                   END
                                   ELSE
                                     IF (ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type" = ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type"::"First Stage Dealer") OR
                                        (ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type" = ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type"::"Second Stage Dealer") AND
                                        (ExciseAsSTUtlisation.CVD = FALSE)
                                     THEN BEGIN
                                       CrSTTakeINDealer :=
                                         CrSTTakeINDealer + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Bed Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SED Amount" +
                                         ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SAED Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."ADET Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."AED(GSI) Amount" +
                                         ExciseAsSTUtlisation."CESS Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."NCCD Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."AED(TTA) Amount" +
                                         ExciseAsSTUtlisation."ADE Amount" ;
                                       CrSTeCessTakeINDealer := CrSTeCessTakeINDealer + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."eCess Amount";
                                       CrSTSHEeCessTakeINDealer := CrSTSHEeCessTakeINDealer + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SHE Cess Amount";
                                     END ELSE BEGIN
                                       CrSTTakeINImporter :=
                                         CrSTTakeINImporter + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Bed Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SED Amount" +
                                         ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SAED Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."ADET Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."AED(GSI) Amount" +
                                         ExciseAsSTUtlisation."CESS Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."NCCD Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."AED(TTA) Amount" +
                                         ExciseAsSTUtlisation."ADE Amount" ;
                                       CrSTeCessTakeINImporter := CrSTeCessTakeINImporter + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."eCess Amount";
                                       CrSTSHEeCessTakeINImporter := CrSTSHEeCessTakeINImporter + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SHE Cess Amount";
                                     END;
                                 UNTIL (ExciseAsSTUtlisation.NEXT = 0);

                               ExciseAsSTUtlisation.RESET;
                               ExciseAsSTUtlisation.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 ExciseAsSTUtlisation.SETRANGE("ECC No.",LocationNo);
                               ExciseAsSTUtlisation.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               ExciseAsSTUtlisation.SETRANGE("RG Record Type",ExciseAsSTUtlisation."RG Record Type"::RG23C);
                               IF ExciseAsSTUtlisation.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF ((ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type" = ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type"::" ") OR
                                       (ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type" = ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type"::Manufacturer) OR
                                       (ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type" = ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type"::"First Stage Dealer") OR
                                       (ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type" = ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Vendor Type"::"Second Stage Dealer")) AND
                                      (ExciseAsSTUtlisation.CVD = FALSE)
                                   THEN BEGIN
                                     CrSTTakeCG :=
                                       CrSTTakeCG + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Bed Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SED Amount" +
                                       ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SAED Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."ADET Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."AED(GSI) Amount" +
                                       ExciseAsSTUtlisation."CESS Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."NCCD Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."AED(TTA) Amount" +
                                       ExciseAsSTUtlisation."ADE Amount" ;
                                     CrSTeCessTakeCG := CrSTeCessTakeCG + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."eCess Amount";
                                     CrSTSHEeCessTakeCG := CrSTSHEeCessTakeCG + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SHE Cess Amount";
                                   END ELSE BEGIN
                                     CrSTTakeCGImporter :=
                                       CrSTTakeCGImporter + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."Bed Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SED Amount" +
                                       ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SAED Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."ADET Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."AED(GSI) Amount" +
                                       ExciseAsSTUtlisation."CESS Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."NCCD Amount" + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."AED(TTA) Amount" +
                                       ExciseAsSTUtlisation."ADE Amount" ;
                                     CrSTeCessTakeCGImporter := CrSTeCessTakeCGImporter + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."eCess Amount";
                                     CrSTSHEeCessTakeCGImporter := CrSTSHEeCessTakeCGImporter + ExciseAsSTUtlisation."SHE Cess Amount";
                                   END;
                                 UNTIL (ExciseAsSTUtlisation.NEXT = 0);

                               // Closing Balance - RG23CPartII
                               CloseCenvatCG := OpenCenvatCG + CrCenvatTakeCG - CrCenvatUsedCG;
                               CloseAEDCG := OpenAEDCG + CrAEDTakeCG - CrAEDUsedCG;
                               CloseOTHCG := OpenOTHCG + CrOTHTakeCG - CrOTHUsedCG;
                               CloseeCESSCG := OpeneCESSCG + CreCESSTakeCG - CreCESSUsedCG;
                               CloseSHeCESSCG := OpenSHEeCESSCG + CrSHEeCESSTakeCG - CrSHEeCESSUsedCG;
                               CloseADETCG := OpenADETCG + CrADETTakeCG - CrADETUsedCG;
                               CloseADCCG := OpenADCCG + CrADCTakeCG - CrADCUsedCG;
                               CloseSTCG := OpenSTCG + CrSTTakeCG - CrSTUsedCG;
                               CloseSTeCessCG := OpenSTeCessCG + CrSTeCessTakeCG - CrSTeCessUsedCG;

                               // Opening Balance - RG23APartII
                               OpenCenvatIN := 0.0;
                               OpenAEDIN := 0.0;
                               OpenOTHIN := 0.0;
                               OpeneCESSIN := 0.0;
                               OpenSHEeCESSIN := 0.0;
                               OpenADETIN := 0.0;
                               RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,StartingDate - 1);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   OpenCenvatIN := OpenCenvatIN + RG23APartII."BED Credit" - RG23APartII."BED Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."SED Credit" - RG23APartII."SED Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."SAED Credit" - RG23APartII."SAED Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."ADET Credit" - RG23APartII."ADET Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit" - RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit";
                                   OpenAEDIN := OpenAEDIN + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit" - RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                   OpenOTHIN := OpenOTHIN + RG23APartII."NCCD Credit" - RG23APartII."NCCD Debit";
                                   OpeneCESSIN := OpeneCESSIN + RG23APartII."eCess Credit" - RG23APartII."eCess Debit";
                                   OpenSHEeCESSIN := OpenSHEeCESSIN + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit" - RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                   OpenADETIN := OpenADETIN + RG23APartII."ADE Credit" - RG23APartII."ADE Debit";
                                   OpenADCIN := OpenADCIN + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit" - RG23APartII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               SerTaxEntryDetail.RESET;
                               SerTaxEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,StartingDate - 1);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 SerTaxEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               SerTaxEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",SerTaxEntryDetail."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               IF SerTaxEntryDetail.FIND('-') THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   OpenSTIN := OpenSTIN + SerTaxEntryDetail."Remaining Credit";
                                   OpenSTeCessIN := OpenSTeCessIN + SerTaxEntryDetail."Remaining Credit (eCess)";
                                   OpenSTSHEeCessIN := OpenSTSHEeCessIN + SerTaxEntryDetail."Remaining Credit (SHECess)";
                                 UNTIL (SerTaxEntryDetail.NEXT = 0);

                               // Credit Availed - RG23APartII
                               CrCenvatTakeINManf := 0;
                               CrAEDTakeINManf := 0;
                               CrOTHTakeINManf := 0;
                               CreCESSTakeINManf := 0;
                               CrSHEeCESSTakeINManf := 0;
                               CrADETTakeINManf := 0;
                               RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE(Type,RG23APartII.Type::Purchase);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",FALSE);
                               IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF ((RG23APartII."Vendor Type" = RG23APartII."Vendor Type"::" ") OR
                                       (RG23APartII."Vendor Type" = RG23APartII."Vendor Type"::Manufacturer)) AND (RG23APartII.CVD = FALSE)
                                   THEN BEGIN
                                     CrCenvatTakeINManf :=
                                       CrCenvatTakeINManf + RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                       RG23APartII."SAED Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit";
                                     CrAEDTakeINManf := CrAEDTakeINManf + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit";
                                     CrOTHTakeINManf := CrOTHTakeINManf + RG23APartII."NCCD Credit";
                                     CreCESSTakeINManf := CreCESSTakeINManf + RG23APartII."eCess Credit";
                                     CrSHEeCESSTakeINManf := CrSHEeCESSTakeINManf + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                     CrADETTakeINManf := CrADETTakeINManf + RG23APartII."ADE Credit";
                                     CrADCTakeINManf := CrADCTakeINManf + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit";
                                   END
                                   ELSE
                                     IF ((RG23APartII."Vendor Type" = RG23APartII."Vendor Type"::"First Stage Dealer") OR
                                         (RG23APartII."Vendor Type" = RG23APartII."Vendor Type"::"Second Stage Dealer")) AND
                                        (RG23APartII.CVD = FALSE)
                                     THEN BEGIN
                                       CrCenvatTakeINDealer :=
                                         CrCenvatTakeINDealer + RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                         RG23APartII."SAED Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit";
                                       CrAEDTakeINDealer := CrAEDTakeINDealer + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit";
                                       CrOTHTakeINDealer := CrOTHTakeINDealer + RG23APartII."NCCD Credit";
                                       CreCESSTakeINDealer := CreCESSTakeINDealer + RG23APartII."eCess Credit";
                                       CrSHEeCESSTakeINDealer := CrSHEeCESSTakeINDealer + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                       CrADETTakeINDealer := CrADETTakeINDealer + RG23APartII."ADE Credit";
                                     END
                                     ELSE
                                       IF (RG23APartII."Vendor Type" = RG23APartII."Vendor Type"::Importer) OR (RG23APartII.CVD = TRUE) THEN BEGIN
                                         CrCenvatTakeINImporter :=
                                           CrCenvatTakeINImporter + RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                           RG23APartII."SAED Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit";
                                         CrAEDTakeINImporter := CrAEDTakeINImporter + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit";
                                         CrOTHTakeINImporter := CrOTHTakeINImporter + RG23APartII."NCCD Credit";
                                         CreCESSTakeINImporter := CreCESSTakeINImporter + RG23APartII."eCess Credit";
                                         CrSHEeCESSTakeINImporter := CrSHEeCESSTakeINImporter + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                         CrADETTakeINImporter := CrADETTakeINImporter + RG23APartII."ADE Credit";
                                         CrADCTakeINImporter := CrADCTakeINImporter + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit";
                                       END;
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE(Type,RG23APartII.Type::Sale);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Vendor Type",RG23APartII."Vendor Type"::" ");
                               IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrCenvatTakeINSReturn :=
                                     CrCenvatTakeINSReturn + RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                     RG23APartII."SAED Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit";
                                   CrAEDTakeINSReturn := CrAEDTakeINSReturn + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit";
                                   CrOTHTakeINSReturn := CrOTHTakeINSReturn + RG23APartII."NCCD Credit";
                                   CreCESSTakeINSReturn := CreCESSTakeINSReturn + RG23APartII."eCess Credit";
                                   CrSHEeCESSTakeINSReturn := CrSHEeCESSTakeINSReturn + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                   CrADETTakeINSReturn := CrADETTakeINSReturn + RG23APartII."ADE Credit";
                                   CrADCTakeINSReturn := CrADCTakeINSReturn + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit";
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               {RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE(RG23APartII."Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",TRUE);
                               IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrSTTakeINManf :=
                                                                               CrSTTakeINManf + RG23APartII."BED Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23APartI
                               I.
                               "S
                               ED
                               D
                               eb

                               t"
                               +
                                     RG23APartII."NCCD Debit" + RG23APartII."ADET Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit" + RG23APartII."ADE Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                   CreCessSTTakeINManf := CreCessSTTakeINManf + RG23APartII."eCess Debit";
                                 UNTIL(RG23APartII.NEXT = 0);   }

                               // Credit Used - RG23APartII
                               CrCenvatUsedIN := 0;
                               CrAEDUsedIN := 0;
                               CrOTHUsedIN := 0;
                               CreCESSUsedIN := 0;
                               CrSHEeCESSUsedIN := 0;
                               CrADETUsedIN := 0;
                               RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE(Type,RG23APartII.Type::Sale);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",FALSE);
                               IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrCenvatUsedIN :=
                                     CrCenvatUsedIN + RG23APartII."BED Debit" + RG23APartII."SED Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."SAED Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23APartII."ADET Debit";
                                   CrAEDUsedIN := CrAEDUsedIN + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                   CrOTHUsedIN := CrOTHUsedIN + RG23APartII."NCCD Debit";
                                   CreCESSUsedIN := CreCESSUsedIN + RG23APartII."eCess Debit";
                                   CrSHEeCESSUsedIN := CrSHEeCESSUsedIN + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                   CrADETUsedIN := CrADETUsedIN + RG23APartII."ADE Debit";
                                   CrADCUsedIN := CrADCUsedIN + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE(Type,RG23APartII.Type::Sale);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",TRUE);
                               IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrCenvatUtilisedServices :=
                                     CrCenvatUtilisedServices + RG23APartII."BED Debit" + RG23APartII."SED Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."SAED Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23APartII."ADET Debit";
                                   CrAEDTTAUtilisedServices := CrAEDTTAUtilisedServices + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                   CrOTHUtilisedServices := CrOTHUtilisedServices + RG23APartII."NCCD Debit";
                                   CreCessUtilisedServices := CreCessUtilisedServices + RG23APartII."eCess Debit";
                                   CrSHEeCessUtilisedServices := CrSHEeCessUtilisedServices + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                   CrADEUtlisedServices := CrADEUtlisedServices + RG23APartII."ADE Debit";
                                   CrADCUtilisedServices := CrADCUtilisedServices + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE(Type,RG23APartII.Type::Sale);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",TRUE);
                               IF RG23CPARTII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrCenvatUtilisedServices :=
                                     CrCenvatUtilisedServices + RG23CPARTII."BED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."SED Debit" +
                                     RG23CPARTII."SAED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23CPARTII."ADET Debit";
                                   CrAEDTTAUtilisedServices := CrAEDTTAUtilisedServices + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                   CrOTHUtilisedServices := CrOTHUtilisedServices + RG23CPARTII."NCCD Debit";
                                   CreCessUtilisedServices := CreCessUtilisedServices + RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit";
                                   CrSHEeCessUtilisedServices := CrSHEeCessUtilisedServices + RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                   CrADEUtlisedServices := CrADEUtlisedServices + RG23CPARTII."ADE Debit";
                                   CrADCUtilisedServices := CrADCUtilisedServices + RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               ServiceTaxDetail.RESET;
                               ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE(Type,RG23APartII.Type::Sale);
                               ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",ServiceTaxDetail."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               IF ServiceTaxDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrServiceTaxUtilisedServices := CrServiceTaxUtilisedServices + ServiceTaxDetail."Service Tax Amount";
                                   CreCessSTUtilisedServices := CreCessSTUtilisedServices + ServiceTaxDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" ;
                                   CrSHEeCessSTUtilisedServices := CrSHEeCessSTUtilisedServices + ServiceTaxDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount" ;
                                 UNTIL (ServiceTaxDetail.NEXT = 0);

                               ServiceTaxDetail.RESET;
                               ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE(Type,RG23APartII.Type::Purchase);
                               ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",ServiceTaxDetail."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               IF ServiceTaxDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrServiceTaxIPServices := CrServiceTaxIPServices + ServiceTaxDetail."Service Tax Amount";
                                   CreCessServiceTaxIPServices := CreCessServiceTaxIPServices + ServiceTaxDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount";
                                   CrSHEeCessServiceTaxIPServices := CrSHEeCessServiceTaxIPServices + ServiceTaxDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                 UNTIL (ServiceTaxDetail.NEXT = 0);

                               STasExciseUtilised.RESET;
                               STasExciseUtilised.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 STasExciseUtilised.SETRANGE("Location E.C. C. No.",LocationNo);
                               STasExciseUtilised.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",STasExciseUtilised."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               IF STasExciseUtilised.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrSTUtilised := CrSTUtilised + STasExciseUtilised."ST as Excise Utilisation";
                                   CreCessSTUtilised := CreCessSTUtilised + STasExciseUtilised."ST eCess as Excise Utilisation";
                                   CrSHEeCessSTUtilised := CrSHEeCessSTUtilised + STasExciseUtilised."ST SHECess Excise Utilisation";
                                 UNTIL (STasExciseUtilised.NEXT = 0);

                               STPaymentECCNo.RESET;
                               STPaymentECCNo.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 STPaymentECCNo.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               STPaymentECCNo.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",STPaymentECCNo."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               IF STPaymentECCNo.FIND('-') THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrSTUtlisedServices := CrSTUtlisedServices + STPaymentECCNo."Credit availed";
                                   CrSTeCessUtilisedServices := CrSTeCessUtilisedServices + STPaymentECCNo."Credit availed (eCess)";
                                   CrSTSHEeCessUtilisedServices := CrSTSHEeCessUtilisedServices + STPaymentECCNo."Credit availed (SHECess)";
                                 UNTIL (STPaymentECCNo.NEXT = 0);

                               // Closing Balance - RG23APartII
                               CloseCenvatIN := OpenCenvatIN + CrCenvatTakeINManf - CrCenvatUsedIN;
                               CloseAEDIN := OpenAEDIN + CrAEDTakeINManf - CrAEDUsedIN;
                               CloseOTHIN := OpenOTHIN + CrOTHTakeINManf - CrOTHUsedIN;
                               CloseeCESSIN := CloseeCESSIN + CreCESSTakeINManf - CreCESSUsedIN;
                               CloseSHEeCESSIN := CloseSHEeCESSIN + CrSHEeCESSTakeINManf - CrSHEeCESSUsedIN;
                               CloseADETIN := CloseADETIN + CrADETTakeINManf - CrADETUsedIN;
                               // CloseSTIN := CloseSTIN + CrSTTakeNManf - CrSTUsedIN;
                               // CloseSTeCessIN := CloseSTeCessIN + CrSTeCessTakeINManf- CrSTeCessUsedIN;

                               // Update PLA amount
                               PLARec.RESET;
                               PLAAmount := 0;
                               PLARec.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 PLARec.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               PLARec.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",PLARec."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer);
                               IF PLARec.FIND('-') THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   PLAAmount :=
                                     PLAAmount + PLARec."BED Credit" + PLARec."AED(GSI) Credit" + PLARec."SED Credit" +
                                     PLARec."SAED Credit" + PLARec."CESS Credit" + PLARec."NCCD Credit" +
                                     PLARec."eCess Credit" + PLARec."Excise Charges Credit" + PLARec."ADE Credit" + PLARec."ADET Credit" +
                                     PLARec."AED(TTA) Credit" + PLARec."SHE Cess Credit";
                                 UNTIL PLARec.NEXT = 0;

                               // Update Invoice Numbers
                               ExciseEntry.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               ExciseEntry.SETRANGE("Document Type",ExciseEntry."Document Type"::Invoice);
                               ExciseEntry.SETRANGE("E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               ExciseEntry.SETRANGE(Type,ExciseEntry.Type::Sale);
                               IF ExciseEntry.FINDFIRST THEN
                                 SlNo1 := ExciseEntry."Document No.";
                               IF ExciseEntry.FINDLAST THEN
                                 SlNo2 := ExciseEntry."Document No.";
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  ClosingCenvat :=
                                    OpenCenvatIN + OpenCenvatCG + CrCenvatTakeINManf +
                                    CrCenvatTakeINDealer + CrCenvatTakeINImporter +
                                    CrCenvatTakeINSReturn + CrCenvatTakeCG + CrCenvatTakeCGImporter +
                                    CrCenvatTakeCGSReturn + CrCenvatTakeIUTransfer -
                                    ((CrCenvatUsedIN + CrCenvatUsedCG )
                                     + CrCenvatUtilisedServices );

                                  ClosingAEDTTA :=
                                    OpenAEDIN + OpenAEDCG + CrAEDTakeINManf + CrAEDTakeINDealer + CrAEDTakeINImporter +
                                    CrAEDTakeINSReturn + CrAEDTakeCG + CrAEDTakeCGImporter + CrAEDTakeCGSReturn +
                                    CrAEDTakeIUTransfer - (CrAEDUsedIN + CrAEDUsedCG) - CrAEDTTAUtilisedServices ;

                                  ClosingNCCD :=
                                    OpenOTHIN + OpenOTHCG + CrOTHTakeINManf + CrOTHTakeINDealer +
                                    CrOTHTakeINImporter + CrOTHTakeINSReturn + CrOTHTakeCG + CrOTHTakeCGImporter +
                                    CrOTHTakeCGSReturn + CrOTHTakeIUTransfer - (CrOTHUsedIN + CrOTHUsedCG) - CrOTHUtilisedServices ;
                                  ClosingADE :=
                                    OpenADETIN + OpenADETCG + CrADETTakeINManf + CrADETTakeINDealer +
                                    CrADETTakeINImporter + CrADETTakeINSReturn + CrADETTakeCG + CrADETTakeCGImporter +
                                    CrADETTakeCGSReturn + CrADETTTakeIUTransfer - (CrADETUsedIN + CrADETUsedCG) - CrADEUtlisedServices ;

                                  ClosingeCess :=
                                    OpeneCESSIN + OpeneCESSCG + CreCESSTakeINManf + CreCESSTakeINDealer +
                                    CreCESSTakeINImporter + CreCESSTakeINSReturn + CreCESSTakeCG + CreCESSTakeCGImporter +
                                    CreCESSTakeCGSReturn + CrCessTakeIUTransfer - (CreCESSUsedIN + CreCESSUsedCG) - CreCessUtilisedServices ;
                                  ClosingSHEeCess :=
                                    OpenSHEeCESSIN + OpenSHEeCESSCG + CrSHEeCESSTakeINManf + CrSHEeCESSTakeINDealer +
                                    CrSHEeCESSTakeINImporter + CrSHEeCESSTakeINSReturn + CrSHEeCESSTakeCG + CrSHEeCESSTakeCGImporter +
                                    CrSHEeCESSTakeCGSReturn + CrSHECessTakeIUTransfer - (CrSHEeCESSUsedIN + CrSHEeCESSUsedCG) - CrSHEeCessUtilisedServices ;

                                  ClosingADC :=
                                    OpenADCIN + OpenADCCG + CrADCTakeINManf + CrADCTakeINDealer +
                                    CrADCTakeINImporter + CrADCTakeINSReturn + CrADCTakeCG + CrADCTakeCGImporter +
                                    CrADCTakeCGSReturn + CrADCTakeIUTransfer - (CrADCUsedIN + CrADCUsedCG) - CrADCUtilisedServices ;
                                  ClosingSTax :=
                                    OpenSTIN + OpenSTCG + CrSTTakeINManf + CrSTTakeCG + CrServiceTaxIPServices + CrSTTakeINDealer +
                                    CrSTTakeINImporter + CrSTTakeCGImporter
                                    - CrSTUtilised - CrSTUtlisedServices;
                                  ClosingeCessOnServices :=
                                    OpenSTeCessIN + OpenSTeCessCG + CreCessSTTakeINManf + CrSTeCessTakeCG + CreCessServiceTaxIPServices +
                                    CrSTeCessTakeINDealer + CrSTeCessTakeINImporter + CrSTeCessTakeCGImporter
                                    - CreCessSTUtilised -
                                    CrSTeCessUtilisedServices;
                                  ClosingSHEeCessOnServices :=
                                    OpenSTSHEeCessIN + OpenSTSHEeCessCG + CrSHEeCessSTTakeINManf + CrSTSHEeCessTakeCG + CrSHEeCessServiceTaxIPServices +
                                    CrSTSHEeCessTakeINDealer + CrSTSHEeCessTakeINImporter + CrSTSHEeCessTakeCGImporter
                                    - CrSHEeCessSTUtilised -
                                    CrSTSHEeCessUtilisedServices;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1500355;1;Column  ;OpenAEDIN___OpenAEDCG;
               SourceExpr=OpenAEDIN + OpenAEDCG }

               SourceExpr=OpenADETIN + OpenADETCG + CrADETTakeINManf + CrADETTakeINDealer + CrADETTakeINImporter + CrADETTakeINSReturn + CrADETTakeCG + CrADETTakeCGImporter + CrADETTakeCGSReturn + CrADETTTakeIUTransfer }

               SourceExpr=OpeneCESSIN + OpeneCESSCG + CreCESSTakeINManf + CreCESSTakeINDealer + CreCESSTakeINImporter + CreCESSTakeINSReturn + CreCESSTakeCG + CreCESSTakeCGImporter + CreCESSTakeCGSReturn + CrCessTakeIUTransfer }

    { 1500489;1;Column  ;ClosingeCessOnServices;

               SourceExpr=OpenAEDIN + OpenAEDCG + CrAEDTakeINManf + CrAEDTakeINDealer + CrAEDTakeINImporter + CrAEDTakeINSReturn + CrAEDTakeCG + CrAEDTakeCGImporter + CrAEDTakeCGSReturn + CrAEDTakeIUTransfer }

    { 4602;1   ;DataItem;<Detailed PLA Entry2>;
               DataItemTable=Table16567;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Challan No.,Challan Date,Document No.)
                                 WHERE(Entry Type=FILTER(Application));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               IF "<Integer4>".Number = 1 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Arrears of Duty under Rule 8",'<>%1',0);
                               IF "<Integer4>".Number = 2 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Other Arrears of Duty",'<>%1',0);
                               IF "<Integer4>".Number = 3 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Interest Payment under Rule 8",'<>%1',0);
                               IF "<Integer4>".Number = 4 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Other interest payments",'<>%1',0);
                               IF "<Integer4>".Number = 5 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Misc. payments",'<>%1',0);
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  PLAEntry2.GET("PLA Entry No.");
                                  IF (PLAEntry2."Posting Date" < StartingDate) OR
                                     (PLAEntry2."Posting Date" > EndingDate) OR
                                     (PLAEntry2."Type of Unit" <> PLAEntry2."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer) OR
                                     ((LocationNo <> '') AND (PLAEntry2."Location E.C.C. No." <> LocationNo))
                                  THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  ChangeCounter := ChangeCounter + 1;
                                  TotalPrintedText := '';
                                  IF  "<Integer4>".Number = 1 THEN BEGIN
                                    TextTobePrinted := 'Arrears of Duty under rule 8';
                                    PLAPaymentAmt := "Arrears of Duty under Rule 8";
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer4>".Number = 2 THEN BEGIN
                                    TextTobePrinted := 'Other Arrears of Duty';
                                    PLAPaymentAmt := "Other Arrears of Duty";
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer4>".Number = 3 THEN BEGIN
                                    TextTobePrinted := 'Interest payment under rule 8';
                                    PLAPaymentAmt := "Interest Payment under Rule 8";
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer4>".Number = 4 THEN BEGIN
                                    TextTobePrinted := 'Other interest payments';
                                    PLAPaymentAmt := "Other interest payments";
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer4>".Number = 5 THEN BEGIN
                                    TextTobePrinted := 'Misc. payments';
                                    PLAPaymentAmt := "Misc. payments";
                                  END;
                                  IF  "<Integer4>".Number = 5 THEN
                                    TotalPrintedText := 'Total';

                                  IF (ChangeCounter > 0) AND (NOT AmountPrinted) THEN
                                    AmountPrinted := TRUE;
                                  PLAPmtAmtTotal := PLAPmtAmtTotal + PLAPaymentAmt;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1500131;2;Column  ;TextTobePrinted     ;
               SourceExpr=TextTobePrinted }

    { 1500135;2;Column  ;PLAPaymentAmt       ;
               SourceExpr=PLAPaymentAmt }

    PROCEDURE InitialiseVariables@1500000();
    BEGIN
      CENVATAmt := 0;
      SEDAmt := 0;
      AEDGSIAmt := 0;
      AEDTTAAmt := 0;
      SAEDAmt := 0;
      CESSAmt := 0;
      NCCDAmt := 0;
      ADETAmt := 0;
      ADEAmt := 0;
      eCESSAmt := 0;
      SHECessAmt := 0;
      Amt := 0;
      QtyRemWithDuty := 0;
    END;

    PROCEDURE CheckRemovedAsSuch@1500001() : Boolean;
    BEGIN
      PostedStrOrderLineDetails.RESET;
      PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Invoice No.",ER1OutputManf."Order No.");
      PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Manually Changed",TRUE);
      PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE(Type,PostedStrOrderLineDetails.Type::Sale);
      PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETFILTER("Document Type",'%1|%2',PostedStrOrderLineDetails."Document Type"::Invoice,
        PostedStrOrderLineDetails."Document Type"::Order);
      PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Tax/Charge Code",'EXCISE');
      PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Tax/Charge Type",PostedStrOrderLineDetails."Tax/Charge Type"::Excise);
      EXIT(PostedStrOrderLineDetails.FINDFIRST);
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function
